</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   TOKYO (AP) -- Tokyo stocks fell sharply early Monday. The Nikkei shed 538.33
points to 16,319.84 points in early trading.
</P>
<SUBHEAD>
Braves 12, Padres 6
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   ATLANTA (AP) -- Brian Jordan homered twice and drove in a career-high seven
runs, Andres Galarraga went 5-for-5 and the Atlanta Braves won for the eight
time in nine games, overpowering the San Diego Padres 12-6 Sunday. Jordan hit a
two-run homer in the sixth to put the Braves ahead for good, then added a
three-run shot in the eighth to eclipse his previous high for RBIs in a game.
</P>
<SUBHEAD>
AP NewsBrief by VINCENT K. WILLIS
