   14. ''Keeping the Faith,'' Disney, $1.12 million, 842 locations,
$1,326 average, $34 million, six weeks.
</P>
<P>
   15. ''Erin Brockovich,'' Universal, $1.1 million, 952 locations,
$1,160 average, $120.2 million, 10 weeks.
</P>
<P>
   16. ''Held Up,'' Trimark, $1.08 million, 679 locations, $1,592
average, $3.4 million, two weeks.
</P>
<P>
   17. ''The Big Kahuna,'' Lions Gate, $791,026, 309 locations,
$2,560 average, $1.2 million, four weeks.
</P>
<P>
   18. ''Final Destination,'' New Line, $683,666, 651 locations,
$1,050 average, $50.8 million, 10 weeks.
</P>
<P>
   19. ''Return To Me,'' MGM, $635,007, 733 locations, $866
average, $30.1 million, seven weeks.
</P>
<P>
   20. ''28 Days,'' Sony, $575,144, 778 locations, $739 average,
$35.4 million, six weeks.
</P>
